cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics techniques to construct 3D virtual garment models from RGB images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics techniques for generating the final 3D model, which suggests the category cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The paper also mentions the use of Virtual Reality and Mixed Reality applications, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper uses a multi-task learning network, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the parsing of semantic parts of the garment, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
